    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It's a lambda expression.</p>\n\n<p>It means that, from the listOfCars, arg0 is one of the items of that list.\nWith that item he is going to do, hence the ->, whatever is inside of the brackets.</p>\n\n<p>In this example, he's going to return a list of cars that fit the condition</p>\n\n<pre><code>Car.SEDAN == ((Car)arg0).getStyle();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
